    <descript>
      <abstract>This polygon layer represents Blockgroup boundary  2000,  Arlington County, VA.  The definition of table data is available via CENSUS_TRACK_Table_2000.</abstract>
      <purpose>2000 Census boundaries represent a hierarchy of statistical areas used to report and summarize demographic information.  Census blocks are the smallest, most basic unit of the census geography.  Blocks are aggregated into block groups, and those in turn into census tracts.</purpose>
    </descript>
